race.description: Commercial Hotel Mixed Stake Pr1 Division1
race.comment: LEKTRA SOLO (7) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (25.84) at Warrnambool. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Can find winning form. SWEET SECRET (6) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at this track, scoring by 1.5 lengths (35.63). Must include in calculations. PENNY PINTO (1) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (23.94) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Rates a winning chance on best. SARAH LOUISE (2) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.
